43:24.970 --> 43:33.910
mean much to me. I don't know whether that means much to you or not, but it's
borosilicate and it is a liquid glass that makes, gives the tile a very hard

43:33.910 --> 43:40.910
surface. You can poke through it with a sharp fingernail or a screwdriver, but
it is, it gives it a hard surface.

43:43.050 --> 43:55.050
And then these are bonded to the, and I'll show you how that's done, is bonded
